<br>
Also, not all evil is focused on destruction and chaos and personal greed.  The Dark Elves and Heretic Erudites both have advanced societies, obviously at least some who are in power look out for what is best for the society as a whole.  Indeed you find much more chaos in the societies (sic) of the halflings, trolls and wood elves.  On most Blue servers a halfling druid is the epitome of evil greed in my opinion...  <p>Lorec <br>
